metadata.description: Vim! gives it a go with a _really_ twisted piece of dark jungle, in his own inimitable style. With influences from Ed Rush to the Digital Hardcore crew. you'll only hear this on MP3, and you'll only get it from Mono211, it's not just a conversion of a 500k XM, it's worth it.. have we sold you yet?
